  "reference_number": "RUS1332",
  "remarks": "\nVladimir EVTUSHENKOV is a prominent Russian businessman and oligarch. EVTUSHENKOV is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by virtue of his ownership of a Sistema JSFC, a conglomerate which has business interests in the Russian energy and information, communications and digital technologies sectors, which are sectors of strategic significance to the Government of Russia. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
